      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "- Rename for commands and options from version 0.5.0\r\n\t- The command and option names were incorrect and have been changed.\r\n\t- ![LGTM](https://img.shields.io/badge/IMPORTANT-red) If you specified the \"Go to previous/next tab\" command setting in version 0.5.0, you need to reconfigure it.\r\n\r\n---\r\n- Rename commands - before → after\r\n\t- `Go to next tab` → `Go to previous tab`\r\n\t- `Go to previous tab` → `Go to next tab`\r\n- Rename options - before → after\r\n\t- `Choose how to go to the previous tab` → `Choose how to go to the next tab`\r\n        - `Back action key` → `Reverse action key`",
